        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <span class="date">Effective Date: January 20, 2026</span>

        <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>Task Master ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how our application accesses, uses, and stores your Google user data.</p>

        <h2>2. Data Access and Use</h2>
        <p>Our application requests access to your Google Calendar data (specifically, the <code>calendar.readonly</code> scope). We use this access strictly for the following purposes:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>To display your upcoming calendar events on your personal dashboard alongside your tasks.</li>
            <li>To help you plan your daily schedule effectively.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We do not use this data for advertising purposes.</p>

        <h2>3. Data Storage</h2>
        <p>We do not store your calendar events on our permanent servers. Calendar data is fetched in real-time or cached temporarily in your local browser storage for performance.</p>

        <h2>4. Data Sharing</h2>
        <p>We do not share, sell, or transfer your Google user data to any third-party tools, AI models, or advertising networks.</p>

        <h2>5. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: <a href="mailto:wer.corp.smarter@gmail.com">wer.corp.smarter@gmail.com</a></p>
